#3 change your environment so that it supports you
annoyed app, filter out e-mail, filter out unhappy party

#4 prepare for the hard situations beforehand
think through the common things that are likely to happen, they're going to blow you and what you will do to respond ?

#5 identity
i am the type of person who goes to the gym. 
i am the type of person who works on their business every single day
if you can connect that pre-existing identity to the action that you want to take
